What did he miss? Because the result represents the defeat of a great favorite that in each presentation showed that she had everything to be the new Miss Colombia, because she had not been elected in vain Queen of Police and Best Face Pretty Vogue, titles obtained by queens Taliana Vargas or Natalia Navarro who took the crown of Miss Colombia.
